    <div class="AssessmentProblem.type">ShortAnswerResponse</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.statement"><p>At a carnival, it costs \$5 for 4 people to play a game. What is the cost per person?</p>&#xD;
</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.solution"><p>Sample responses:</p>&#xD;
&#xD;
<ul>&#xD;
	<li>It costs \$1.25 per person to play a game.</li>&#xD;
	<li>The carnival charges \$1.25 per person for a game.</li>&#xD;
</ul>&#xD;
